                Oxford's unique character as a college town creates specific flooring challenges - from 
                high-traffic student areas to seasonal occupancy patterns. We've developed specialized 
                approaches for university facilities, student housing, and the businesses that serve 
                this academic community, ensuring durability through intense use periods and easy 
                maintenance during quieter times.
              </p>
              
