                academic years and quieter summer periods. We schedule our Oxford concrete coating 
                projects to minimize disruption during busy academic periods while taking advantage 
                of optimal installation conditions during breaks and summer months.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="content-column">
              <h3>Featured Oxford Projects</h3>
              
              <div class="project-highlight">
                <h4>Miami University Area Student Housing</h4>
                <p>
