                  moisture barrier technology for basement application, and subtle texture finish that 
                  echoed the home's original architectural details.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <strong>Result:</strong> Perfect integration with the home's historic character while 
                  solving long-standing moisture and durability issues in the basement and garage areas.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
